# blocks are organised into block-groups.
# to start a group, start a line with "=" followed by a name.
# to end a group, simply have a line consisting of "=".

= my daily blocks
# constrain your blocks in time by using the '@' symbol. this constraint will block the
# group from 12:00 until 13:00.
@ 12:00 - 13:00
# you can have multiple constraints, but they can't overlap.
#
# you can make time spans 'wrap around' midnight too. for instance, this constraint will
# leave the group *un*blocked from 06:00 until 18:00.
@ 18:00 - 06:00

# list of sites to block. "www." variants are added automatically.
reddit.com
facebook.com
twitter.com
=


= my weekly blocks
# you can make weekday-based constraints too, via the first three letters of the day.
# like the time-only constraints, these shouldn't overlap.
@ mon 00:00 - fri 23:59
@ sat 20:00 - sat 23:59

# you can have time-only & day-based constraints at the same time.
@ 23:00 - 06:00

youtube.com
twitch.tv
=
